---
// src/pages/about.astro
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Me | The Fault In My Writings"
  description="Learn more about faulty and their interests in programming, low-level systems, and more."
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    
    <section class="about-content">
      <p>
        I'm faulty. I like everything programming and a few other things.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        After messing around with quite a few languages and in quite a few different fields, I feel 
        like I have finally found my calling. Although, the realization could have come sooner instead 
        of when I'm about to finish my <b>Bachelor of Computer Engineering</b>. But better late than never right?
      </p>
      
      <p>
        <b><i>What is that calling you might be asking?</i></b><br>
        If I were to describe it in a single word, it would be "<b>Low-Level</b>". 
        I don't exactly know what specifically I mean by "Low-Level", but I'm leaning towards 
        <b>Operating Systems</b>. I also have interest in <b>RISC-V, programming languages theory and compilers,
        distributed systems</b>.
        <br>
        I do have some interest in AI as well but the FOMO and the fear that it progressed so far ahead are 
        balancing each other out.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        In terms of programming languages, the list of the ones I like are even more long but I've choosen
        Rust and C to be my primary languages of choice.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Other than programming, what I like is very limited. I like reading books (mostly fiction).
        I also like reading mangas and watching animes.
        Lastly, as you might have guessed from the existence of this blog, I also like writing.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #1e293b;
  }

  .about-content {
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: #1e293b;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content b {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #4f46e5;
  }

  .about-content br {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>